channel.title: I need help with making a server
channel.description: I really need help on making a server and I read the tutorial I downloaded satan's isle went to no-ip.com made an account there and I did all that stuff. I probably did something wrong on No-ip.com and I don't know how to make my own IP. Can someone help me? I'm the only one allowed on the server but I will have to be on like 127.0.0.### or something like that. So is there a way to actually change the whole IP. Thanks[br][size=1]Posted on: June 14, 2007, 05:55:36 PM[/size][hr]I make you admin on the server if you are right. And plus another special secret prize.
